Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.20,0:00:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.54,0:00:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guest is, make me please pin badge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.50,0:00:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same as one you brought.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.13,0:00:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who asked you to make the pin badge, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.22,0:00:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of man was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.30,0:00:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.80,0:00:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.14,0:00:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.64,0:00:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barrel Titor?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.06,0:00:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Titor?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.19,0:00:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. Just like barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.73,0:00:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like barrel...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.40,0:00:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Japanese word for barrel is "taru"!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.15,0:00:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taru?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.07,0:00:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A while back, it was in a Rai-Net anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.24,0:00:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was this barrel-like monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.91,0:00:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.79,0:00:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a taru.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.75,0:00:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or balloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.71,0:00:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man like a barrel or a balloon?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.46,0:00:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where can we contact him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.38,0:00:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.67,0:00:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Private information.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.38,0:00:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.68,0:01:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(983,0)}No clues, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.01,0:01:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if the man's pin badge is finished,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.77,0:01:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,won't he pick it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.02,0:01:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He told the man it would take a week to make,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.52,0:01:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he left without placing the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.98,0:01:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we have to give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.15,0:01:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.28,0:01:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still one way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.32,0:01:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I wait for the time leap machine's completion tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.16,0:01:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and go back in time...
