Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.59,0:03:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Suzuha?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't she just leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.51,0:03:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.15,0:03:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I forgot to ask when the man was coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.78,0:03:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is that him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.57,0:03:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was right. The silhouette is like a barrel or a balloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.91,0:03:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.62,0:03:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you decide to get a fake pin badge?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:42.55,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it suck if she couldn't find her dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.55,0:03:45.05,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,So I figured I'd show her the badge
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.05,0:03:47.55,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,and make a fake Titor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.55,0:03:49.52,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,So you wanted to get her excited over nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:52.89,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two types of lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:55.52,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Lies that hurt, and lies that don't{\fscx80}-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:03:59.32,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think Suzuha would want that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.95,0:04:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Amane told me not to tell anyone this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.16,0:04:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That time machine can only travel backward.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.71,0:04:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you go, you can't return.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.80,0:04:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you brought me an ice-cold zero-calorie cola!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.35,0:04:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we fix the time machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.07,0:04:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even working this whole time, that's still amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daru's the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.16,0:04:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to judge him by his looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.82,0:04:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he looks unhealthy and kind of dim...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I've changed my mind about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:05:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you help me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, in the steaming hot confines of the time machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.50,0:05:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can forget our shame and take off our clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daru-kun and Suzu-san look good together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm saying this because
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'll ever have the chance to say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.94,0:05:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really grateful to you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I first came here, I didn't know anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though this era is much more peaceful,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,somehow, to me, it was really scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.62,0:05:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now I have lots of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really happy that I could come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I could spend time with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really had fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I could be a lab member,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.51,0:05:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I could spend time with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:06:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once you go, you can't return.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe Rintarou!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change the future{\fscx80}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.61,0:06:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure to change the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.11,0:06:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make it a free world, like this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe Rintarou?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.03,0:06:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you regret the memories you've made?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having to say goodbye, do you think that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would have been better if we'd all never met?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.96,0:06:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you regret it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.09,0:06:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hashida Itaru told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's worried about you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.98,0:06:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Changing the future was my father's wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you don't care what will happen to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.52,0:06:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The '70s weren't a bad time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make friends like you there, and I'll live freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.42,0:07:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.84,0:07:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's fine, but give it a final check.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.14,0:07:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.39,0:07:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be happier...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just fixed a time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1975...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.86,0:07:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what month and day I should go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's good for this? Taiankichijitsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.32,0:07:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or Tomobiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.57,0:07:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those days are for weddings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.28,0:07:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Tomobiki might be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.33,0:07:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could help you make new friends faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends? That would be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FG204?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Suzu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.26,0:08:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what my dad named the time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.19,0:08:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it might fit
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if we removed the tires.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.74,0:08:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really like it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.83,0:08:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.16,0:08:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii figured out who your dad is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.17,0:08:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.42,0:08:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they're right nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always felt
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you two make a good pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you're father and daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You can't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.99,0:08:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzu-san's dad is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.00,0:09:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The idea of this pervert getting married...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.04,0:09:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Isn't that a little mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.79,0:09:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you come to this conclusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, "barrel" means "taru," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taru... Daru... Daru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.85,0:09:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Okarin and Barrel Titor
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were also part of the group that helped found the resistance, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.61,0:09:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in 2010, Akihabara, they were working on a time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they knew about Okarin's Reading Signer...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.99,0:09:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reading Steiner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They knew about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That only leaves Daru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, the most convincing proof Mayushii found was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.71,0:09:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name of the time machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.75,0:09:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FG204.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a future gadget.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.97,0:09:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A future gadget?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:10:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's stuff to the right of it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Future Gadget 204,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2nd Edition, Ver. 2.31"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That naming convention...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.49,0:10:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You should say, "Papa!" at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be a pervert right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.88,0:10:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in the time machine you made.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do what you attempted,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.02,0:10:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so watch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:11:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.78,0:11:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.08,0:11:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.54,0:11:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was your mom cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a short one, with a baby face and big boobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.18,0:11:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep that a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.43,0:11:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget about Mayushii and the rest of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.81,0:11:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.11,0:11:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find IBN 5100.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.15,0:11:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll get it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please, change the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you in thirty-five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it'll only be a few hours for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.88,0:12:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:18.86,Celly,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1\fscy80\be1\fs30\frz338.387\3c&H4A3A41&\c&H4A3A41&\pos(691,171)}AAAAAAA
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:18.86,Celly,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs23\pos(710,174)\frx20\fry2\frz336.477}Part-Time Warrior
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:18.86,Celly,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs23\pos(741,218)\frx14\fry2\frz337.126}Thank You
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:18.86,Celly,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs23\frx20\fry0\pos(539,196)\frz336.507}Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.57,0:12:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be sure we see each other again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep working hard until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you try, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1774,0)}We've received word that the satellite that fell
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.07,0:12:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on the Akihabara Radio Building has vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you think this pin badge could be our initials?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:12:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe's "O."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.56,0:13:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hashida's "H."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina's "S."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.65,0:13:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then "M" is Makise. And "A" is Amane, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lab member badge, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to make one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.62,0:13:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Divergence Meter hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it change after Amane brings us the IBN 5100 or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuha's fifty-four now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.55,0:13:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My daughter's over thirty years older than I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.68,0:13:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She might be married, with grandkids.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So at this age, I could see my own great-grandkids?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should act really grown-up, like a great-grandfather!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.69,0:13:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.62,0:13:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Braun?
