Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.70,0:14:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:07.87,Handwriting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(544,207)\frz322.635}Hashida \NSuzu
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hashida Suzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that from Suzu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.17,0:14:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.96,0:14:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a letter from someone who once took care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She asked me to give it to you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.39,0:14:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She died.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:30.39,Handwriting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1502)\move(544,207,535,188)}{\an8\move(544,207,524,185)\frz322.635\t(0,4443,\fscx120\fscy120)}Hashida \NSuzu
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.31,0:14:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.48,0:14:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okabe Rintarou-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.23,0:14:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's been so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.61,0:14:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's me, Amane Suzuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.65,0:14:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It may have only been a few hours to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but right now, it's June 13th, 2000.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll get straight to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I failed. I failed. I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I failed. I failed. I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I failed. I failed. I have failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.01,0:15:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I failed. I failed. I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.43,0:15:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I only remembered who I was a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.77,0:15:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the past twenty-four years, I'd forgotten myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.15,0:15:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time travel didn't work right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The repair job was imperfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.28,0:15:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it wasn't my dad's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I should have gone directly to 1975.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.79,0:15:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I shouldn't have stopped in 2010.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I shouldn't have been so selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, the future won't change!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't get an IBN 5100.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.31,0:15:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why have I even lived this long?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I forgot my duty and spent my life doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.78,0:16:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forgive me! Forgive me! Forgive me! Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:08.91,Celly,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1\frz345.071\3c&H4C3C45&\c&H4C3C45&\fscy110\t(500,2127,\fscy120\fscx125)\move(728,272,979,250,500,2127)}AAAAAAAAA
