Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okabe Rintarou, when I tried to go to 1975,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.33,0:16:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}after the time machine forum meeting, you stopped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.79,0:16:13.83,Celly,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\be2\pos(211,482)\frz353.3266}Do not give in to your assistant's threats.\NFollow Suzuha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because of the rain that night, the time machine broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.63,0:16:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you can go back in time,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.97,0:16:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I ask that you not stop me back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My life...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.14,0:16:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...was wasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.57,0:16:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Braun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.45,0:16:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.41,0:16:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me how Hashida Suzu-san died.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:16:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you care?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.92,0:17:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to know how she died!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how it was,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't seem like simple curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what's your relationship to Suzu-san, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A long-ago acquaintance...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.36,0:17:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I still remember
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our time together well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.78,0:17:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't want to say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She hanged herself in her home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For about a year before she died,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.91,0:17:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she was mentally unstable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But up until then,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,768)}she was a cheerful, kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time machine broke because
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.11,0:18:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I stopped her back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.95,0:18:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd never sent that D-mail,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she'd have gone to 1975 then!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.12,0:18:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin...
