Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin, are you sending a D-mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, all of this will disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the time we remember spending
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with Suzu-san won't have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So please, change the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.25,0:19:08.17,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Hashida Suzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:10.17,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't heard that name in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:12.63,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:13.84,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.84,0:19:16.47,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, is she still...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.47,0:19:19.60,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's been ten years...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She really looked after me for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've liked to have seen her at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she commit suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.32,0:19:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She died of an illness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I live in her house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bike...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.12,0:19:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she always really loved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't throw it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.46,0:19:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So for ten years, I've kept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.09,0:19:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At first, she and I were neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, one day,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.68,0:19:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my house burned down in a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.43,0:20:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.31,0:20:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she let me stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.27,0:20:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was she alone that whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.52,0:20:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She never married...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was a little strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once, I asked her
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.07,0:20:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why she'd done all this for someone with no relationship to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.74,0:20:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then she laughed, and she said this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.29,0:20:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Everyone gets help
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.79,0:20:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from someone else, at some point in their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So someday, you should help someone, too."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.88,0:20:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.05,0:20:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One second...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzu-san had this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what the number means?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.56,0:20:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was always looking at it, from her hospital bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.48,0:20:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Is this the number before it changes? Or after?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.44,0:20:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I manage to change it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.61,0:20:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever it was, it bothered her to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.99,0:21:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The divergence number changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.16,0:21:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it hasn't gone beyond 1%.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.58,0:21:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The train for the outer line will arrive shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Please stand behind the yellow line.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.54,0:21:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Yamanote Line is working at this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.84,0:21:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.98,0:21:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:43.16,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.16,0:21:44.70,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.66,0:21:50.62,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mayushii's phone rang. Was that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.00,0:21:53.58,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,She was having a nice nap, so I didn't wake her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.51,0:22:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Suzuha... Did the world change?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Has Mayuri been saved?

